module.exports = {
    writeFiles,
    files
};
 
 
function writeFiles() {
    mkdirp(MAIN_SRC_DIR);
    this.copy('angularjs/gulp/_handle-errors.js', 'gulp/handle-errors.js'); // to avoid interpolate errors
    // write angular 1.x files
    this.writeFilesToDisk(files, this, false, 'angularjs');
}
